N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 611.11 - Continuity of powers

State Regulations

Nothing contained in this Part shall
be construed to limit the powers of the Appellate Division or the presiding
justice thereof or the administrator of the assigned counsel plan otherwise
granted pursuant to law. Notes
